div.p: Dendrogram obtained from the agglomerative hierarchical cluster analysis of 68 Foeniculum vulgare essential oil compositions. (CT1) anethole-rich chemotype, (CT1a) anethole chemotype, (CT1b) anethole/limonene chemotype, (CT1c) anethole/camphor chemotype, (CT2) estragole chemotype, (CT3) estragole/α-phellandrene chemotype, (CT4) anethole/estragole/α-pinene chemotype, (CT5) α-phellandrene chemotype, and (CT6) limonene/β-pinene/myrcene chemotype.
